{"tid":1397653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷工] 想罷又唔敢罷嘅人，請加入早上不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-02T14:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T10:34:31.000Z","uid":288778,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93e81e7c98212367b4cb7c65cb1dc072e617c9fa","tid":1397653,"uid":288778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"好多人內心好支持罷工<br />\n但又怕公司秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n請呢類巴絲打一定一定要加入 早 上 不 合 作 運 動！<br />\n塞爆港鐵 巴士！<br />\n咁大家就可以一齊唔返、返唔到<br />\n一齊減低罷工成本<br />\n等更多打工仔可以加入！<br />\n<br />\n一、照著返工衫，冇人可以唔俾你上車！<br />\n<br />\n二、以各種方式不合作，例如：<br />\n<br />\n跌文件<br />\n倒瀉奶<br />\n等車企第一排<br />\n等車 等車 再等車<br />\n企出啲<br />\n攞一袋二袋<br />\n<br />\n三、打工仔可自由加入，時間flexible，輪流齊齊塞<br />\n<br />\n我知嚴格咁唔算罷工<br />\n但絕對係由淺入深，由易至難咁支持緊罷工！"},{"pid":"4a83b2ee305ed48e64728da115ab342c96e160ed","tid":1397653,"uid":288385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"推爆！我都吾想，但真係番吾到公司門口！"},{"pid":"01b90950b47700acf0bea4df5fbab43a4e9c3c2d","tid":1397653,"uid":146696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:21:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好鍾意返工 可惜入唔到地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b579d0b118184a06225238112774e3c2589c71ac","tid":1397653,"uid":227303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"上左地鐵落唔到車"},{"pid":"4a73163222e3beb4d0fc53a4b4a53e6f0740f3a2","tid":1397653,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eadc70a6a1c663cba6e1271935b7d8ae2921f9","tid":1397653,"uid":38301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"[8月5日]請想